('Asvine Pen', 'Milton, ON', 100, true, 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'These fresh, elegant, reliable forest series fountain pen by Asvine is a true marriage of the sophistication of finer days with the latest technology of modern times. Hand assembled and checked for flawless quality, it gives high precision and exceptional writing comfort for every occasion, coupled with a gorgeous design. With this pen in your possession, clients, colleagues, and friends will know you for your taste, class, and sophistication.', 1),
