('CocomK Blue Plier Hand-held Stapler', 'Calgary, AB', 400, false, 'Stapler picture', 'Stapler picture', 'Stapler picture', 'Stapler picture', 'Powerful hand-held stapler holds 20 sheets stapling capacity at a time. Also work perfect to staple on hardboard, cardbaod, plastic bag, brown paper and any other hard paper. Meets all the daily office and home use needs and work for long lasting high frequency use.', 7),
('Fockety Green Hand-held Stapler', 'Calgary, AB', 400, false, 'Stapler picture', 'Stapler picture', 'Stapler picture', 'Stapler picture', 'This stapler can easily determine the binding position, ergonomic handle is comfortable to grip and convenient for one-handed operation. Safe and environmentally friendly stapleless stapler, a new concept in the field of staplers, you can use in any occasion, and children do not have to worry about hurting their hands.', 9),
('Scriveiner Pen', 'Milton, ON', 150, false, 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'These fresh, elegant, reliable forest series fountain pen by Asvine is a true marriage of the sophistication of finer days with the latest technology of modern times. Hand assembled and checked for flawless quality, it gives high precision and exceptional writing comfort for every occasion, coupled with a gorgeous design. With this pen in your possession, clients, colleagues, and friends will know you for your taste, class, and sophistication.', 4),
('Novium Hoverpen 2.0', 'Oakville, ON', 350, false, 'Pen picture', 'Pen picture', 'Hoverpen 2.0 was designed to function and to impress. Highly precise craftsmanship of the pedestal has the Hoverpen sitting in a ring of magnetic repulsion. Balancing against at a 23.5 degree angle, the pen itself is engineered to take a stand against gravity itself. The way it defies gravity makes it impossible to ignore.', 6),
('Mileseey Laser Measuring Tape', 'Edmonton, AB', 200, false, 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Laser distance extends to 229ft. MiLESEEY laser measuring tape generates a point/dot that is up to 3X brighter than red beams. This digital tape measure with green-beam allows you to measure in long distance even in super bright days, easy to see and measure, becomes an easy one-man task. Soft and safe to eyes: laser class: Class 2, laser type: 490-560nm, <1mW.', 10),
('Brown Tape Measure', 'Regina, SK', 200, false, 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Measuring Tape picture', 'Measuring Tape picture', '60-Inch sewing tape measure is lightweight and accurately printed in both inches and centimeters, squeeze retractable, Small Leather tape measure very comfortable in the PALM of the Hand, Perfect for sewing, body measuring, fabric measuring and more.', 8),
('Herb Kitchen Scissors', 'Winnipeg, MB', 400, false, 'Scissors picture', 'Scissors picture', 'Scissors picture', 'Scissors picture', 'Monochef herb mincer, made of food grade stainless steel, 5 sharp blades fixed firmly by 3 rivets, durable and safe. Just 1 pair of scissors but installed 5 pairs of blades working at the same time, makes chopping easier and much more efficient than a knife or single blade scissors. Sharp blades make fast leaves snipping rather than crushing or messing. Guarantee no flavor losing of ingredients.', 3),
('Sewing Scissors', 'Winnipeg, MB', 600, false, 'Scissors picture', 'Scissors picture', 'Scissors picture', 'Scissors picture', 'Our versatile right hand scissors heavy duty is made from industrial grade materials –Premium High Carbon Steel- which is stronger, harder and stays sharp longer than the standard stainless steel used in other so called high quality shears. Each blade is durable, solid and has Razor Edge Retention that helps it stays sharp, even after running through the toughest materials, fabrics and leather.', 5);
